{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106271, "create_time": 1652111128, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "第6天全部自杀", "timestamp": 1652111128}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106272, "create_time": 1652111207, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 那么请问如果旅行者说的是“你们这里有蓝眼睛的人”呢", "timestamp": 1652111207}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106277, "create_time": 1652111306, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "旅行者被土著们烤着吃了", "timestamp": 1652111306}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106281, "create_time": 1652111378, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "请问如果旅行者在第二天捅死了一个红眼睛的人，之后自杀还会发生吗", "timestamp": 1652111378}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106283, "create_time": 1652111397, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 为什么呢？", "timestamp": 1652111397}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106284, "create_time": 1652111477, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 第5天全部自杀", "timestamp": 1652111477}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106289, "create_time": 1652111782, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 请问如果旅行者在第二天捅死了三个红眼睛的人，之后自杀还会发生吗", "timestamp": 1652111782}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106290, "create_time": 1652111811, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 为什么呢", "timestamp": 1652111811}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106303, "create_time": 1652112113, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "旅行者说的不是废话吗？岛上的所有人本来就知道有红眼", "timestamp": 1652112113}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106306, "create_time": 1652112167, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 你可以用只有两个红眼睛的情况分析一下，旅行者的话是有意义的", "timestamp": 1652112167}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106336, "create_time": 1652113333, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "tzx经典问题", "timestamp": 1652113333}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106340, "create_time": 1652113406, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 这个问题我其实一直在思考，如果只有一个红眼睛，那旅行者的话有信息量，如果有多个红眼睛的话就没有信息量。但是递推好像没有问题，问题出在哪儿呢？", "timestamp": 1652113406}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106347, "create_time": 1652113533, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "根据第三条，不应该是只有红眼睛的人自杀吗？", "timestamp": 1652113533}, {"author_title": "毛毛语", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106353, "create_time": 1652113659, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "应该是第五天晚上红眼睛全部自杀吧，而且5个人情况下似乎旅行者的话确实没含金量", "timestamp": 1652113659}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106354, "create_time": 1652113663, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "我高考完在知乎上看了这个，现在我研究生快毕业了", "timestamp": 1652113663}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106355, "create_time": 1652113672, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "我高考完在知乎上看了这个，现在我研究生快毕业了", "timestamp": 1652113672}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106359, "create_time": 1652113775, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 两个红眼睛也有信息量，因为每个红眼会认为另一个红眼不知道岛上有红眼睛的人", "timestamp": 1652113775}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106363, "create_time": 1652113956, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Alice: 为什么第六天蓝眼睛也自杀呢？", "timestamp": 1652113956}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106365, "create_time": 1652114031, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "蓝眼睛对自身自杀的判断会比红眼晚一天，所以红眼自杀后蓝眼睛应该都活下来了", "timestamp": 1652114031}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106367, "create_time": 1652114222, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Jason: 规则里没说蓝眼睛的人要自杀啊", "timestamp": 1652114222}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106370, "create_time": 1652114374, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Grace: 啊我意思是判断自己是不是红眼", "timestamp": 1652114374}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106375, "create_time": 1652115083, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "这个问题核心有一个子非鱼的结构", "timestamp": 1652115083}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106410, "create_time": 1652116318, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Francis: 这句话的信息量在于让所有人都知道“所有人都知道岛上有红眼睛”这件事。当然一次嵌套可能还不够，甚至也能让所有人都知道“所有人都知道‘所有人都知道有红眼睛’这件事”这件事...可以一直嵌套无限层。这个信息是改变一切的关键。", "timestamp": 1652116318}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106412, "create_time": 1652116389, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "还是非常喜欢这种经典的题目，洞主有没有类似的其他题目呢？", "timestamp": 1652116389}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106546, "create_time": 1652121275, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re Kate: 所有人不是本来都知道“所有人都知道岛上有红眼睛”这件事吗？大家肯定不知道红眼的确切数量不然红眼早都自杀了，所以多出了什么信息？", "timestamp": 1652121275}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106591, "create_time": 1652123317, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "假设我是红眼，我知道红眼数量为4或5而不可能是1，那么第一天本就不可能有人自杀，从无人自杀的事实不能说明任何东西，逻辑链从这就已经断了，无人自杀", "timestamp": 1652123317}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106624, "create_time": 1652124845, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re Louis: （也就是说，必不会发生的事情没有发生不能作为后续任何依据，第二晚跟第一晚根本没区别，后续推导也都不成立）事实上这个推导只在有一个或两个红眼时有效，三个红眼以上就不可能死人了。", "timestamp": 1652124845}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106657, "create_time": 1652140491, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 13, "text": "Re Louis: 可能区别在于那句“缜密的推理”，应该指岛上每个人都推理能力一流，并会不断试图去推理到底还有几个红眼睛\n但问题是这些人要真这么严谨，不早自杀了，还得等人跟他们说？", "timestamp": 1652140491}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106839, "create_time": 1652153404, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 14, "text": "Re Louis: 三个红眼时，如果前两天晚上都没死人，那么红眼的人就知道岛上不止两个人红眼，所以这三个都会自杀", "timestamp": 1652153404}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106844, "create_time": 1652153644, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "\n给五个红眼睛标个号ABCDE，假如我是A，那么在没有旅行者之前，我不知道B知道C知道D知道E知道岛上有红眼睛，在旅行者之后，我知道B知道C知道D知道E知道岛上有红眼睛", "timestamp": 1652153644}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106849, "create_time": 1652154008, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 14, "text": "Re 洞主: 为什么蓝眼睛的会自杀呢，既然前一天自杀了一批人，难道不能说明岛上没有红眼睛的人吗", "timestamp": 1652154008}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106850, "create_time": 1652154111, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Nathan: 蓝眼睛不会自杀", "timestamp": 1652154111}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106861, "create_time": 1652154636, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 14, "text": "Re 洞主: 以为昨晚Alice说的是对的", "timestamp": 1652154636}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106872, "create_time": 1652154951, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Louis: 洞主11点半发的那条是我想说的。", "timestamp": 1652154951}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 106942, "create_time": 1652156580, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re Nathan: 三个红眼而我是其中之一，那么我知道红眼要么2个要么3个。第一晚没死人让我和其他两个红眼知道红眼不是1个，但这个信息显然是无效的。也就是说，第二天晚上不再能排除2个，因为后面每天都是Day 1而不是Day 2.", "timestamp": 1652156580}], "create_time": 1652110927, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1652154951, "likenum": 16, "n_attentions": 16, "n_comments": 34, "pid": 38460, "poll": null, "reply": 34, "text": "#树洞智商测试\n红眼睛和蓝眼睛：一个岛上有100个人，其中有5个红眼睛，95个蓝眼睛。这个岛有三个奇怪的宗教规则。\n\n1.他们不能照镜子，不能看自己眼睛的颜色。\n\n2.他们不能告诉别人对方的眼睛是什么颜色。\n\n3.一旦有人知道了自己是红眼睛，他就必须在当天夜里自杀。\n\n某天，有个旅行者到了这个岛上。由于不知道这里的规矩，所以他在和全岛人一起狂欢的时候，不留神就说了一句话：【你们这里有红眼睛的人。】\n\n问题：假设这个岛上的人每天都可以看到其他所有人，每个人都可以做出缜密的逻辑推理，请问岛上会发生什么？", "timestamp": 1652110927}}